entries.s_3: Greetings soldier! I'm in charge of supplies for our battle weary troopers. I have several orders en route and the longer you can keep the Imperial forces out of here, the more supplies will become available.
entries.s_4: Move along, citizen. This is not the place for a civilian!
entries.s_5: I understand commander, what's in stock right now?
entries.s_6: I understand commander; I will do my best in aiding the defenses!
entries.s_7: Let me show you my current inventory. < Pop up SUI here >
entries.s_8: Sounds good soldier, for the Alliance!
